{"word":"Zerubbabel","slug":"zerubbabel","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Zerubbabel</b> <a href=\"#/H2216\">H2216</a><br/><a href=\"#/H2217\">H2217</a> <br/> Called also Sheshbazzar.<br/> Directs the rebuilding of the altar and temple after his return from captivity in Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=8'>Ezr 3:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=4&verse=3'>Ezr 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=5&verse=2'>Ezr 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=5&verse=16'>Ezr 5:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=1&verse=14'>Hag 1:14</a><br/> Leads the emancipated Jews back from Babylon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=1&verse=11'>Ezr 1:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=2'>Ezr 2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12'>Neh 12</a><br/> Appoints the Levites to inaugurate the rebuilding of the temple<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=3&verse=8'>Ezr 3:8</a><br/> Prophecies relating to<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=37&chapter=2&verse=2'>Hag 2:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=38&chapter=4&verse=10'>Zec 4:10</a><br/> Called Zorobabel in the genealogy of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=1&verse=12'>Mat 1:12</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=27'>Luk 3:27</a>"}]}